**Visual Patterns:** 8–15 images typical for editorial posts; 20–36 for listicles. Mostly Instagram/Pinterest embeds, not editorial photography.

**Recommended Image Count:** 12–16 images — this is a pillar guide covering multiple sub-aesthetics; visual range matters more than quantity.

